window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A possessive dragon shifter. A girl determined to kill him. A fated connection they can’t deny.</p> <p>Lenora Tashe is nothing special.</p> <p>Which is why the village decides to sacrifice her to the obsidian dragon that’s been terrorizing them for decades.</p> <p>But Lenora has her own plan. She’s going to stop the dragon shifter from ever threatening her homeland again—or die trying.</p> <p>What she doesn’t count on is the fact the dragon spends half his time as a man who can be as infuriating or as seductive as he pleases.</p> <p>And when he discovers Lenora isn’t just some simple village girl but actually his fated mate, the one creature that can withstand his dragon flame and calm the beast within?</p> <p>Things begin to heat up…</p> <p>To Wed an Obsidian Villain is a spicy enemies-to-lovers fantasy romance with a heroine who has nothing to lose and a dragon who loves nothing more than spoiling his human, performed in dual narration</p>"; 
